                    "value": "<p>A @Template[type:emanation|distance:20] of spiritual energy pushes against intruders, as though trying to drive their souls away. Each creature in the area takes @Damage[8d6[spirit]] damage depending on a @Check[type:will|dc:29] save.</p>\n<p>The clay effigy can't Cast Out again for [[/br 1d4 #Recharge Cast Out]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and @Damage[3d6[persistent,spirit]] damage. The persistent damage ends if the creature moves over 60 feet from the clay effigy or the effigy is destroyed.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, except the persistent damage is increased to @Damage[6d6[persistent,spirit]].</p>"
